Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair和Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在ES成員中除名了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.00,0:01:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是2056454
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT驅逐艦Preamps和LSU Canopus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.30,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情况 我們要求立刻進入直綫跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.90,0:02:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK 這裏是控制臺 請進入跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.90,0:02:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過 Preamps和LSU Canopus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况變得很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須闖過這關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 這是我們的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一個男孩對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 下個月就5歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就應該對他進行教育了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他無論如何也不要到GOTT任職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會這麽做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也要我能活著回去後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射後2分15秒進入亞空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登記被注銷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 被整肅了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十二話 死生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5分24秒後我們將進入Zero星系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果順利 我們也許可以躲過總部的搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幷且藏到某個殖民地去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的一個是LAV-78
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去這裏沒什麽問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移民率87%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政治立場中立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也比較容易獲得港口停靠許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣不就成了逃亡者了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法啊 事實正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登記被注銷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是宇宙行星聯合政府當局的正式通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須對你下這個命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長已經對我們下達了整肅令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上司與部下之間的信賴關係已經完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生漫長 會發生很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是像你們倆 有漫長的人生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是自己想活這麽長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麽味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太在意她們倆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tweedledum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是貪婪的 因此才是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這是很有趣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都曾經做過永生之夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但當他們得到了永生時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們却說自己幷不想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.20,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你總是如此 置身事外 當第三者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我是監察官 這是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想開槍打我 請便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不會佩服你這種浪費子彈的行爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是由官方渠道發布的整肅令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SO成員一隊或二隊肯定會追擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據目前的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.30,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內務13課可能已經完成了部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內務第13課？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.90,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 也就是所謂的GOTT整肅部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來\N我們差不多該决定吃下一頓晚餐的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們真的想活下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也該進行補給了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麽認爲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她們覺得自己能逃掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們就會試試看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對她們感到有點同情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不這麽想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是對追她們的人更感到同情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的Earl Gray啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香氣適宜 不會妨礙品嘗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時我爲那兩人特地買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應過她們兩個回來後請她們喝的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間長了味道就淡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞掃帚只能增添垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工具沒用了就應該丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.80,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個被丟弃的工具可能就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細檢查別出錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微小的錯誤可能會導致喪命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長有話要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此次作戰的目標是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.80,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ES成員Eclair和Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.90,0:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過本隊僅限于\N鎮壓危險分子時才准予戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是將用談判的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此次任務不是以整肅行動爲優先嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.00,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會使你們全員平安的回到Aineias
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有責任由身爲隊長的我來承擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力在緊盯目標上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要有任何輕率的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.00,0:07:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談判的鐵則就是耐心交涉以求和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.60,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都無權去破壞一個5歲男孩的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下個月才5歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員 立刻進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3分鐘後亞空間脫出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.10,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 算了 至少補給食物吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說他說得那麽難聽 他太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.80,0:08:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只不過是履行監察官的職責罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 沒有好茶招待…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來點葡萄酒如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 這個很好喝 謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一見他就有氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.90,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裏悠閑的時候 他還在工作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該稍微感謝他才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這麽說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該把怒氣發泄在貴族身上\N而不是他和局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我沒辦法像你那樣想得開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？被整肅？她們倆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.10,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太蠢了 小Ec真是個處事笨拙的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這盤通心粉是不是咖喱放多了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經抵達LAV-78
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前時間1346
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本局應該已經通知過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關閉認證信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從標準降落場西北方進入通用碼頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從西北方的通用碼頭進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來…竟然下整肅命令啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 我們獲准使用D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是內務13課的人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是內務13課的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你不會讓我們輕鬆地逃走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲在程序上 我們必須確認你們的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以選擇投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由詢問會來决定是非對錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想問那個的話 我們的回答是NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然連你們都派來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在詢問會上勝算很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們爲什麽不攻擊我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是綜合戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內務13課只是用來牽制我們的先頭部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能是在等第一或第二小隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常上下關係分得那麽清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候反而團結起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那說明他們是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算她自己抹去了記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却還是在重複相同的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使過了1000年 華爾茲還是華爾茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種旋律沒有變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我已經補給完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要離開了 快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你們倆的樣子 他們應該已經到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯 趕快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特殊小隊 到前排！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第二小隊的SO成員勞拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間1643 根據總部的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你們開始實行逮捕程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗對雙方都不好 請你們投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拒絕呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在重申一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特殊小隊 啓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 那可不是普通的拘束綫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經啓動了連接處的起爆裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.30,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們反抗 連接處就會分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內部的生化雷管會反應幷爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣大小的殖民星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概會被炸掉一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太胡鬧了 如果那樣的話 你們也會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以我們才請你們投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們的生命掌握在你們兩個手裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們會有一段時間\N不能吃這裏的料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們會變得很忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair會求饒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 怎麽可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在將部下的性命置于危險之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不公平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不也是一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當你們逃跑時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.90,0:14:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們挾持了宇宙行星聯盟的監察官作爲人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你們的罪狀之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你把我們的位置通知了他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是貪婪的 因此才是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這是很有趣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想開槍打我 請便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不會佩服你這種浪費子彈的行爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不希望你們死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我們還是决絕呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在任何情况都有辦法存活下來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了那時 很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能啓動D指令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D指令在未啓動前 沒有對付的辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 能來得及嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拘束綫被無效化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤索夫 啓動D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這和我們的約定不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.60,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 談判破裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤索夫 啓動D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 特殊小隊 啓動D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請輸入數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23620679
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D指令啓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D指令是使它們體內的納米細胞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是納米機械 强制膨脹的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.60,0:17:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擴張的細胞會壓迫內部器官直至摧毀它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哪些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此你爲什麽還有啓動它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因爲那是我們的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爲了保衛組織 必須有人去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們做了肮髒的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且通過做這樣的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.40,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的家人才可以\N每年平安的慶祝他們的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Mist…疫苗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須使它發揮抗體的效用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 來不及了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他們已經活了很長的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們仍然很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒有毀掉她們未來的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙行星聯盟的ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在注入抗體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經暫時停止了她內部的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許他的全部記憶會因此而被喚醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能會很殘酷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也比死掉要好
